{"type": "article", "id": 5582, "title": "Pebble 手表", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-27T07:42:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234022VApRiG3H7yhkECbO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tPebble 是丹麦设计工作室 KiBiSi 的第一个手表作品,受丹麦手表品牌 Jacob Juul 之邀进行设计。独特的非对称的表盘灵感来自于斯堪的纳维亚海滩上平滑的鹅卵石，带来一种平衡与细腻的审美体验。“为什么手表不是方的就是圆的？这个问题就是我们展开这次设计的出发点。” KiBiSi 的创始人 Lars Larsen 说。Pebble 采用注塑模制硅环制成的表盘结构，搭配意大利真皮表带、不锈钢表壳以及防刮蓝宝石玻璃。定价 190－237.50 英镑（约合人民币 1777－2222 元）不等，<a href=\"http://www.dezeenwatchstore.com/shop/pebble-black-black/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340204gZvkULocuqsr9KH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234020JMjrPKw07f1QTc2A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234021VNtPvor1KAkYDxRi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234021MPu9oapn4tIRrdLy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}